data.description: Gorgeous Merrill Ranch single level 3BD/2BA, 3 car garage home! Beautiful gourmet open concept kitchen w/stainless steel appliances, granite counter tops, tile backsplash, gas cooktop, double ovens & center island. Family Room filled w/natural light & custom shelving space, canned lights & ceiling fan. The entire home has tile flooring for easy maintenance. The primary bedroom boasts wood look tile floors, custom shutters, canned lights & a ceiling fan. The ensuite primary bathroom boasts oversized custom tiled walk in shower, dual sinks & large walk in closet. The secondary bedrooms are spacious & also include beautiful custom shutters & generous closets. Buy today in desired Anthem at Merrill Ranch Communit
